text: Palmetto is an unincorporated community in Oglethorpe County, in the U.S. state of Georgia. ==History== The community was named for palmetto trees near the original town site. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Oglethorpe County, Georgia Category:Unincorporated communities in Georgia (U.S. state)
title: Palmetto, Oglethorpe County, Georgia
